---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About — ErgoFresco"
	description="ErgoFresco helps remote workers in warm climates build comfortable, ergonomic home offices."
>
	<section class="about">
		<div class="container">
			<header class="page-header">
				<h1>About ErgoFresco</h1>
				<p class="lead">
					We help remote workers in warm climates build home offices
					that are comfortable, ergonomic, and actually worth sitting
					in all day.
				</p>
			</header>

			<div class="prose">
				<h2>Why ErgoFresco?</h2>
				<p>
					Most ergonomics advice ignores one critical variable: heat.
					When your home office hits 30°C, the best lumbar support in
					the world won't save your productivity. We test and review
					gear with warm climates in mind — because that's the reality
					for millions of remote workers.
				</p>

				<h2>What we cover</h2>
				<p>
					Desk fans, mesh chairs, standing desks, cooling pads, and
					everything in between. If it makes your workspace cooler or
					more comfortable, we cover it.
				</p>

				<h2 id="affiliate">Affiliate disclosure</h2>
				<p>
					ErgoFresco participates in affiliate programs including
					Amazon Associates. When you purchase through our links, we
					may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This
					never influences our recommendations — we only recommend
					products we would genuinely use ourselves.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 780px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1.5rem;
	}

	.page-header {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		padding-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.65;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.prose h2 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
		padding-top: 1rem;
	}

	.prose p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.prose a {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.prose a:hover {
		color: var(--accent-dark);
	}
</style>
